spc / speedwalkcommand        Adds a speedwalk command to the current recording
 
   Format:
      ;spc <cmd>              Adds a speedwalk command
 
   Notes:
      Adds a speedwalk command to the current recording, which will be 
         automically removed later (unless the recording is saved as a mission).
      (If you need to preserve spacing, enclose the command with diamond
          brackets <...>)
      See the help for the ';record' command for more information about
         recordings.
 
   User commands:
      spc / speedcmd / speedcommand / speedwalkcommand
